00:57:50.836 --> 00:57:54.481
maybe occasionally chimp twins
do happen, but it's not been

00:57:54.481 --> 00:57:56.239
reported that I've seen.
 

00:57:56.239 --> 00:57:59.360
Anybody take a--
Student:  Not about

00:57:59.360 --> 00:58:01.637
twins, I was just going to ask
if that's regulated by hormones

00:58:01.637 --> 00:58:02.159
completely.
 

00:58:02.159 --> 00:58:06.849
Like you would say that
lactation stops--

00:58:06.849 --> 00:58:07.780
Prof: Yes.
 

00:58:07.780 --> 00:58:11.547
Student:  But it's a
